{"tid":2263610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(港豬系列)147萬人認購螞蟻　凍資近1.3萬億破紀錄","createTime":"2020-10-30T04:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T14:58:08.000Z","uid":156363,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"56feb3fff14ffeb26222e336528d891b3921fef2","tid":2263610,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"螞蟻集團H股今日中午截止認購。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，截止11時，公開認購人數達到147萬人，凍結資金近1.3萬億港元，打破上月上市的農夫山泉凍資逾6700億元紀錄，以人數計，亦超過2006年工行近100萬人認購記錄。<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻集團預計在下月5日上市，入場費4040元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557457-20201030.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557457-20201030.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=7544fdc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557457-20201030.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=90429f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557457-20201030.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6051d9b81ee434501698091f546f6d638db164a6","tid":2263610,"uid":127425,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"成班大陸燦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7854252f748ee5086b2499971ff430d6a61d46d","tid":2263610,"uid":270506,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"147萬人中咗龐茲騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb53fe223a9fbfb42